内容</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">法律文书论证方法</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">论证顺序</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">法院必读文书</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(95, 156, 239); box-sizing: border-box;">二、请求抗辩归纳技术</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">不同审级请求抗辩归纳</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">举证意见= 证明依据 + 证明方法 + 证明对象 + 关联性</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">质证意见 = 否定性质证意见 + 否定理由</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(95, 156, 239); box-sizing: border-box;">三、规范的法律文书格式</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(95, 156, 239); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">民事起诉状</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">证据清单</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(95, 156, 239); box-sizing: border-box;">四、法律文书示范</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">李律师法律服务报告演示</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(95, 156, 239); box-sizing: border-box;">五、新工具</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(95, 156, 239); box-sizing: border-box;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">客户沟通方式</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">云存储共享工具</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">印象笔记</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(95, 156, 239); box-sizing: border-box;">六、李律师笔记演示</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="color: rgb(14, 14, 14); box-sizing: border-box;">李律师历年笔记演示</span></p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 10px 0%; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; min-width: 10%; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 0px 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">05</p></section></section></section><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block; min-width: 10%; max-width: 100%; vertica